documentation.text: Sealed Bid auction protocol.
@dev Emitted when contract receives token.
@dev Emitted when `account` makes a secret offer of `hashString`.
@dev Emitted when auction states moves to RECEIVEINF_OFFERS.
@dev Emitted when `accounts` reveals offer of `price` and `secret`
@dev Emitted when owner reveals minimum price `amaount`.
@dev Emitted when `account` wins the auction for an offered `amount`
@dev Emitted when owner get payed `amount`
@dev Emitted when `account` is reinbursed `amount`
@dev Emitted when `account` retrives ERC721.

@dev Auction constructor 
 Constructs the auction contract.
 Requirements:
  
  -'_nftContract' cannot be zero address

@dev Transfers ERC721 to contract
 
 Requirements:
  -Auction state must be CONTRACT_CREATION
 Emits a {ERC721Transfer} event.

@dev Lets a participant make an offer
 
 Requirements:
  -Auction state must be RECIVEING_OFFERS
  -Contract owner cant make an offer
  -Must transfer a non zero amount of eth
 Emits a {OfferMade} event.

@dev Changes state of auction to offer reveals
 
 Requirements:
  -Time origin must be larger than contract set time
  -Auction state must be in RECIVEING_OFFERS
  -Must transfer a non zero amount of eth
 Emits a {OffersClosed} event.

@dev Reveals offer of participants
 
 Requirements:
  -   accountToAmount[_msgSender()] must not be zero
  -   accountToOffer[_msgSender()] must be zero. Prevents double reveals
  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL
  -   Must transfer a non zero amount of eth
  -   _amount must be equal or smaller to accountToAmount[_msgSender()]
  -   _secret and _amount hash must match stored hash
 Emits a {OfferRevealed} event.

@dev Changes auction state to CALCULATING_WINNER
 
 Requirements:
  -   caller must not be owner
  -   time origin must be larger than preset closeReveals time
  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL
 Calls _closeReveals() Internal funciton.

@dev Owner reveals minimum price and calculates winner
 
 Requirements:
  -   caller must be owner
  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL
  -   time origin must be larger than preset closeReveals time
  -   _secret and _amount hash must match stored hash
 Emits a {MinimumPriceRevealed} event.

@dev Closes reveal period and calculates winner, intenal
 
 Emits a {WinnerChosen} event.

@dev Auction owner retrives sale price or nft if it did not sell
 
 Requirements:
  -   caller must be owner
  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED
 Emits a {OwnerPayed} xor {TokenWithdrawal} event.

@dev Reinburses deposited amount left to participants after auction ends
 
 Requirements:
  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED
  -   accountToAmount[_msgSender()] must be larger than 0
 Emits a {ParticipantReimbursed} event.

@dev Auction winner retrives ERC721 token.
 
 Requirements:
  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED
  -   caller must be auction winner
 Emits a {TokenWithdrawal} event.

MinimumPriceRevealed(uint256).details: Emitted when owner reveals minimum price `amaount`.

OfferMade(address,bytes32).details: Emitted when `account` makes a secret offer of `hashString`.

OfferRevealed(address,string,uint256).details: Emitted when `accounts` reveals offer of `price` and `secret`

OffersClosed().details: Emitted when auction states moves to RECEIVEINF_OFFERS.

WinnerChosen(address,uint256).details: Emitted when `account` wins the auction for an offered `amount`

closeOffers().details: Changes state of auction to offer reveals  Requirements:  -Time origin must be larger than contract set time  -Auction state must be in RECIVEING_OFFERS  -Must transfer a non zero amount of eth Emits a {OffersClosed} event.

closeReveals().details: Changes auction state to CALCULATING_WINNER  Requirements:  -   caller must not be owner  -   time origin must be larger than preset closeReveals time  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL Calls _closeReveals() Internal funciton.

constructor.details: Auction constructor  Constructs the auction contract. Requirements:    -'_nftContract' cannot be zero address

makeOffer(bytes32).details: Lets a participant make an offer  Requirements:  -Auction state must be RECIVEING_OFFERS  -Contract owner cant make an offer  -Must transfer a non zero amount of eth Emits a {OfferMade} event.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

ownerGetsPayed().details: Auction owner retrives sale price or nft if it did not sell  Requirements:  -   caller must be owner  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED Emits a {OwnerPayed} xor {TokenWithdrawal} event.

reimburseParticipant().details: Reinburses deposited amount left to participants after auction ends  Requirements:  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED  -   accountToAmount[_msgSender()] must be larger than 0 Emits a {ParticipantReimbursed} event.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

revealOffer(string,uint256).details: Reveals offer of participants  Requirements:  -   accountToAmount[_msgSender()] must not be zero  -   accountToOffer[_msgSender()] must be zero. Prevents double reveals  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL  -   Must transfer a non zero amount of eth  -   _amount must be equal or smaller to accountToAmount[_msgSender()]  -   _secret and _amount hash must match stored hash Emits a {OfferRevealed} event.

transferAssetToContract().details: Transfers ERC721 to contract  Requirements:  -Auction state must be CONTRACT_CREATION Emits a {ERC721Transfer} event.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

winnerCalculation(string,uint256).details: Owner reveals minimum price and calculates winner  Requirements:  -   caller must be owner  -   Auction state must be in OFFER_REVEAL  -   time origin must be larger than preset closeReveals time  -   _secret and _amount hash must match stored hash Emits a {MinimumPriceRevealed} event.

winnerRetrivesToken().details: Auction winner retrives ERC721 token.  Requirements:  -   Auction state must be in AUCTION_ENDED  -   caller must be auction winner Emits a {TokenWithdrawal} event.
